{"sections":{"main":{"type":"article-template","custom_css":[".article .section-header__title {text-transform: none;}",".pbo .section-header {margin-bottom: 0;}",".pbo {padding-bottom: 20px;}"],"settings":{"image_hero":false,"blog_show_tags":true,"blog_show_date":false,"blog_show_comments":true,"blog_show_author":false,"social_sharing_blog":false}},"rich_text_QW67Qx":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_c6XTVm":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p>Jewelry is more than just an accessory - it is a statement of identity, refinement, and craftsmanship. In the world of luxury, the details define the man, and the choice of jewelry speaks volumes. <br\/>From the bold allure of black diamond pendants to the understated elegance of men’s 18k gold rings, investing in fine jewelry is not simply about aesthetics; it is about embracing quality, longevity, and a design philosophy that transcends fleeting trends.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_c6XTVm"],"custom_css":["h3 {text-transform: none;}","@media screen and (max-width: 640px) {.main-block {margin-top: 0; }}"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"text_columns_dWCUhq":{"type":"text-columns","blocks":{"text_block_ch7mDX":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGOR0024-01BVW_7_1.png","image_mask":"square","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"","style_link":false,"chat_btn":false,"button_label":"","button_link":""}},"text_block_cg3Fwf":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GIAN0910-01YE_7_1.png","image_mask":"square","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"","style_link":false,"chat_btn":false,"button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["text_block_ch7mDX","text_block_cg3Fwf"],"name":"t:sections.text-columns.presets.text_columns_with_images.name","settings":{"title":"","btntext":"","btnurl":"","text":"","align_text":"center","divider":false,"mobile_link":""}},"rich_text_VpbM4X":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_BCBwCT":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<h3>A Legacy of Craftsmanship and Material Excellence <\/h3><p>The difference between high-end pieces and mass-produced accessories lies in the composition and the craftsmanship. Marco Dal Maso jewelry, for example, is meticulously designed using <strong>luxury metals and precious stones<\/strong>, and handmade by skilled artisans who uphold the traditions of fine Italian jewelry-making. <br\/><strong>Gold and diamonds<\/strong> do not tarnish or lose their value. Men’s gold bracelets in 18k, men’s 18k gold ring or a black diamond cross necklace offer an opulence that withstands time, aging with elegance.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_BCBwCT"],"custom_css":["h3 {text-transform: none;}"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"background_image_text_YWkhD6":{"type":"background-image-text","name":"t:sections.background-image-text.presets.large_image_with_text_box.name","settings":{"classes":"custom-banner-img","subtitle":"","title":"","text":"","text_color":"#000000","button_label":"","button_link":"","bg_color":"#000000","btn_color":"#ffffff","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GIAN0851-01YEEN-still_1_1.png","mobile_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GIAN0851-01YEEN-still_1_1.png","layout":"center","height":550,"framed":false,"parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"top","lazyload_images":true}},"rich_text_mPdLmH":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_pLp69r":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<h3>Investment-Worthy Elegance<\/h3><p>Unlike disposable trends, high-end jewelry retains its value, often becoming heirloom pieces that are passed through generations. The weight of a men’s 18k bracelet, the precision of a diamond gladiator ring, the rare brilliance of a black gold cross necklace—these are not mere adornments but investments in artistry and legacy.<br\/>In an era of fast fashion and impermanence, true luxury lies in permanence. Men’s Italian jewelry, with its impeccable heritage of design, stands as a testament to this philosophy. <br\/>By investing in men’s Italian jewelry, you are choosing craftsmanship over mass production, timeless style over passing trends.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_pLp69r"],"custom_css":["h3 {text-transform: none;}"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"background_image_text_arFJQC":{"type":"background-image-text","name":"t:sections.background-image-text.presets.large_image_with_text_box.name","settings":{"classes":"custom-banner-img","subtitle":"","title":"","text":"","text_color":"#000000","button_label":"","button_link":"","bg_color":"#000000","btn_color":"#ffffff","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GICL0982-01YEEN-still_1.png","mobile_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GICL0982-01YEEN-still_1.png","layout":"center","height":550,"framed":false,"parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"top","lazyload_images":true}},"rich_text_UJkxLK":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_T7XzgC":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<h3>A Distinctive Presence for Every Occasion <\/h3><p>Luxury jewelry transitions seamlessly between everyday wear and special occasions. A men’s silver hoop earring or a double leather bracelet adds effortless sophistication to a casual look, while a men’s luxury fine ring enhances formal attire.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_T7XzgC"],"custom_css":["h3 {text-transform: none;}"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"produc